 SetAPen grey220
  print If you want to destroy a strong inanimate object with pure force, it is best to make your creatures
 setapen grey240
  print  work togheter
 setapen grey220
  print  to take it down.  A single creature attacking alone is often futile.
  print
  print
  print The same goes for powerfull enemy creatures.  Ganging up on a dragon will bring it down easier than you might think.
